\id ZEC
\h Zakariyya 
\toc1 Zakariyya 
\toc2 Zakariyya 
\toc3 Zak. 
\mt1 Zakariyya  
\c 1
\s1 Ařaɣi i ttubet  
\m
\v 1 \bd Deg uyur wiss tmenya, deg useggʷas wiss tmenya n Dariyus\bd*, yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Zakariyya, mmis n Baraxya, mmis n Ɛiddu, anabi, inna:   
\b  
\m
\v 2 “SIDI tuɣa iffugem aṭṭas x řejdud nwem.  
\v 3 Ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: Dweř-dd ɣari, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, xenni Necc ad ɣarwem-dd dewřeɣ, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.  
\v 4 War ttiřim am řejdud nwem i yinni umi barrḥen inabiyyen n zic, nnan: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, dewřem-dd xenni zeg ibriden nwem iɛeffnen u zi tmegga nwem iɛeffnen!’ Maca nitni war sřin ca u war d ayi wcin amezzuɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Ica. 31:6; Irm. 3:12; 18:11; Ḥiz. 18:30; Ḥuc. 14:2\x*  
\v 5 Řejdud nwem, mani ǧan? U inabiyyen, ma ad ddaren i řebda?  
\v 6 Maca awařen inu d tweṣṣa inu nni umureɣ i imsexxaren inu, inabiyyen, ma war řqifen řejdud nwem? Nitni dewřen-dd, nnan: Am mammec tuɣa SIDI n řɛeskarat inekkʷa ad yegg akidneɣ ɛlaḥsab ibriden nneɣ d tmegga nneɣ, ammu i igga Netta akidneɣ.’” \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt Igjd. 1:18\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tameẓriwt tamezwarut - Arebɛa n iysan  
\m
\v 7 \bd Deg wass wiss arebɛa u-ɛicrin, deg uyur wiss ḥiṭac, wa d ayur n Cabaṭ, deg useggʷas wiss tnayen n Dariyus\bd* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Zakariyya, mmis n Baraxya, mmis n Ɛiddu, anabi, ḥima ad \add kis\add* issiweř.   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Necc ẓriɣ di ǧiřet, xzar, aqa ijj n weryaz x ijj n uyis d azeggʷaɣ. Netta tuɣa ibedd jar tcejjura n triḥant di řaǧaɣ u awarni as din iysan izeggʷaɣen d \add yeysan\add* iqarqacen d \add yeysan\add* icemřařen.  
\v 9 Necc nniɣ: “Sidi inu, min ɛnan ina?” \add Řexdenni\add* inna ayi lmalak nni kidi issawařen: “Necc ad ac ssecneɣ min ɛnan ina!”  
\v 10 Aryaz nni ibedden jar tcejjura n triḥant, yarra-dd, inna: “Ina d inni dd-issekk SIDI ḥima ad suḥen x temmurt.”  
\v 11 Nitni arrin-dd x lmalak n SIDI, wenni ibedden jar tcejjura n triḥant, nnan: “Neccin nsuḥ di temmurt, u xzar, marra tammurt teqqim, tarsa.”   
\b  
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd lmalak n SIDI, inna: “\add A\add* SIDI n řɛeskarat, ař meřmi \add ɛad\add* war tᵉttḥinnid x Urcalim u x tneddam n Yahuda nni x tuɣa tsexḍed sebɛin n iseggʷusa-ya?”  
\v 13 SIDI yarra-dd x lmalak nni kidi issawařen \add s\add* wawařen cnan, \add s\add* wawařen n ufewwej.  
\v 14 Lmalak nni kidi issawařen, inna ayi: “Barreḥ, ini:  
\b  
\m \bd ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd*  
\m \qt Necc usmeɣ di ṭṭweɛ n Urcalim\qt*  
\m \qt d Ṣihyun s wasam d ameqqran.\qt*   
\m
\v 15 \qt S ijj n uduqqez ameqqran n weɣḍab inu\qt*  
\m \qt ffugmeɣ x řegnus innefxen.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc tuɣa ffugmeɣ mɣir cwayt n řweqt,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maca\+tl* nitni ruḥen arnin dayes.’\qt*   
\m
\v 16 \qt S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI:\qt*  
\m \qt ‘Necc dewřeɣ-dd ɣar Urcalim s teḥnunect,\qt*  
\m \qt Taddart inu ad tᵉttwabna dayes,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu\+tl* i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat,\qt*  
\m \qt uca \+tl a\+tl*fiřu n řeɛbar\qt*  
\m \qt ad ittwagg x Urcalim.’\qt*   
\m
\v 17 Arni barreḥ, ini:  
\b  
\m \bd ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd*  
\m \qt Tineddam inu ad feyyḍent ɛawed s řxar,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar SIDI ad issfewwej Ṣihyun ɛawed\qt*  
\m \qt u Netta ad ixḍar Urcalim ɛawed.’”\qt*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss tnayen - Arebɛa n iccawen d arebɛa n imziřen  
\m
\v 1 Necc ssgeɛɛdeɣ tiṭṭawin inu uca ẓriɣ, u xzar \add aqa din\add* \bd arebɛa n waccawen\bd*.  
\v 2 Necc nniɣ i lmalak nni kidi issawařen: “Min ɛnan ina?” Netta yarra-dd xafi: “Ina d arebɛa n waccawen nni izzuzaren Yahuda, Israil d Urcalim.”   
\m
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* isscen ayi SIDI \bd arebɛa n imziřen\bd*.  
\v 4 \add Řexdenni\add* necc nniɣ: “Min umi dd-usin nitni, min ɣa ggen?” Netta issiweř, inna: “Ina d accawen nni izzuzaren Yahuda, ařami war dd-issgeɛɛed \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj azeǧif nnes, maca ina usin-dd ḥima ad ten ssnexřɛen, ḥima ad nḍaren accawen n řegnus nni dd-issgeɛɛden icc ḍidd i temmurt n Yahuda ḥima ad tt zuzzaren.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss třata - Aryaz s ufiřu n řeqyas  
\m
\v 5 Necc ssgeɛɛdeɣ tiṭṭawin inu, ẓriɣ, u xzar, aqa \add din\add* ijj n weryaz s ufiřu n řeɛbar deg ufus nnes.  
\v 6 Necc nniɣ: “Mani ɣa traḥed cek?” Netta yarra-dd “\add Necc ad raḥeɣ\add* ḥima ad ɛbareɣ Urcalim maḥend ad ẓareɣ mecḥař \add teǧa\add* tiru nnes u mecḥař \add teǧa\add* tuzzeggart nnes.”  
\v 7 U xzar, iffeɣ-dd lmalak nni kidi issawařen uca ijj n lmalak nneɣni iffeɣ-dd ḥima ad kides immeřqa,  
\v 8 inna as: “Deɣyet, siweř ak-d uḥudri nni, ini:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Urcalim ad din tiři\qt*  
\m \qt teccur s tneddam nurrzment břa řeḥyuḍ\qt*  
\m \qt zi ssibbet n waṭṭas n iwdan d řmař\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl i iǧan\+tl* di řwesṭ nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 9 \qt Necc ad as iřiɣ d ijj n řḥiḍ n tmessi\qt*  
\m \qt i d as-dd ittennḍen, iqqar SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt u di řwesṭ nnes ad as iřiɣ i uɛuǧi.\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 \qt Deɣyam, deɣyam, arewřem\qt*  
\m \qt zi temmurt n ccamal,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu i\+tl* iqqar SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar Necc bḍiɣ kenniw\qt*  
\m \qt am arebɛa n isemmiḍen n ujenna,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu i\+tl* iqqar SIDI.\qt*   
\m
\v 11 \qt Deɣyat, Ṣihyun, fekket,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl cem\+tl* d tenni izeddɣen\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar yeǧis n Babil!’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 \bd “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd*  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Di ṭṭweɛ n uɛuǧi,\qt*  
\m \qt issekk ayi-dd Netta ɣar řegnus\qt*  
\m \qt nni zzaysen ttwakeccḍem,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar wenni kenniw i ɣa iḥadan,\qt*  
\m \qt iḥada mummu n tiṭṭ inu.\qt*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Maɣar xzar, Necc ssenhezzeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt afus inu xasen,\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad dewřen d takeccaḍt\qt*  
\m \qt n imsexxaren nsen.\qt*  
\m \qt Kenniw ad tessnem\qt*  
\m \qt aqa issekk ayi-dd SIDI n řɛeskarat.\qt*   
\m
\v 14 \qt Sřiwřew u farḥ, \+tl a\+tl* yeǧis n Ṣihyun,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar xzar, Necc ad dd-aseɣ\qt*  
\m \qt u ad zedɣeɣ di řwesṭ nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu\+tl* i iqqar SIDI.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Lawi 26:12; Ḥiz. 37:27; 2 Kur. 6:16\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 \bdit ‘Deg wass nni,\bdit*  
\m \qt ad qqnen waṭṭas n řegnus ɣar SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad iřin d řgens inu.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc ad zedɣeɣ di řwest nnem\qt*  
\m \qt u ad tessned, aqa SIDI n řɛeskarat\qt*  
\m \qt issekk ayi-dd ɣarem.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Izhd. 22:1 Bṭ. 2:9\x*   
\m
\v 16 \qt SIDI ad iṭṭef Yahuda d tasɣart nnes\qt*  
\m \qt x temmurt iqeddsen.\qt*  
\m \qt Netta ad ifarz Urcalim ɛad.\qt*   
\m
\v 17 \qt Ejj marra ddat ad isseɣd\qt*  
\m \qt zzat i wudem n SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar Netta ifaq-dd\qt*  
\m \qt zi Tzeddiɣt nnes Iqeddsen.’”\qt*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss arebɛa- Akehhan ameqqran Yahucaɛ  
\m
\v 1 \add Awarni as\add* isscen ayi Yahucaɛ, arrays n ikehhanen. Netta tuɣa ibedd zzat i wudem n lmalak n SIDI. Cciṭan ibedd-dd ɣar ufus afusi n Yacuɛa ḥima ad zzayes isscetca.  
\v 2 SIDI inna i cciṭan: “Ad yiři ad cek iɛaqeb SIDI, \add a\add* cciṭan! Ad cek iɛaqeb SIDI, wenni ifarzen Urcalim! Ma war iǧi \add Yahucaɛ wanita\add* d ijj n ukeccuḍ qeřɛen t-dd zi tmessi?” \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Yah. 9\x*  
\v 3 Yahucaɛ tuɣa yarḍ arruḍ iwessxen am ibedd zzat i wudem n lmalak.   
\m
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* iṭṭef Netta deg wawař uca issiweř ak-d yinni ibedden zzat i wudem nnes, inna: “Kksem as arruḍ iwessxen i wanita!” \add Xenni\add* inna as: “Xzar, Necc kkseɣ zzayek řmuɛṣiyyet nnec u ad cek ssyarḍeɣ s ijj n warruḍ icuwwaren.” \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt Mixa 7:18\x*  
\v 5 Necc nniɣ: “Ad as qqnen ict n areẓẓet tamezdagt x uzeǧif nnes!” U nitni qqnen as areẓẓet tamezdagt x uzeǧif nnes uca ssyarḍen as arruḍ \add icuwwaren\add*, am tuɣa lmalak n SIDI ibedd din  
\v 6 \add Xas uca\add* iched lmalak n SIDI i Yahucaɛ, inna:   
\b  
\m
\v 7 \bd “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd*  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Mařa cek tuyured x ibriden inu,\qt*  
\m \qt u mařa cek ad teḥḍid tasexxart inu,\qt*  
\m \qt xenni ad tessuyured\qt*  
\m \qt uřa d Taddart inu s řḥeqq\qt*  
\m \qt u ad tiřid d ameḥḍay n řemraḥat inu,\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad ac wceɣ\qt*  
\m \qt ad tzemmared ad traḥed ad tadfed\qt*  
\m \qt jar inni da ibedden.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Xenni seř, Yahucaɛ,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl cek,\+tl* arrays n ikehhanen,\qt*  
\m \qt cek d imeddukkař nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt inni iqqimen zzatek,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar nitni d ict n řeɛřamet n utebhet,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar xzar, Necc ad dd-awyeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt Amsexxar inu, ‘AƔEDDU’.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:8 \xt Ica. 4:2; 11:1; Irm. 23:5; 33:15; Zak. 6:12\x*   
\m
\v 9 \qt Maɣar xzar, aẓru,\qt*  
\m \qt wenni din ssarseɣ zzat i Yahucaɛ,\qt*  
\m \qt x weẓřu nni \+tl xezzarent\+tl* sebɛa n tiṭṭawin.\qt*  
\m \qt Xzar, Necc ad \+tl dayes\+tl* neqceɣ\qt*  
\m \qt taneqqact nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu\+tl* i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat,\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad kkseɣ\qt*  
\m \qt řmuɛṣiyyet n temmurt-a\qt*  
\m \qt deg ijj n wass!\qt*   
\m
\v 10 \bdit Deg wass nni,\bdit* \qt iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat,\qt*  
\m \qt ad tɛarḍem ijj i wenneɣni\qt*  
\m \qt sadu tzayart u sadu wartu.’”\qt*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss xemsa - Řqendiř d tnayen n tzitunin  
\m
\v 1 Lmalak nni kidi issawařen, iɛqeb-dd uca issfaq ayi-dd am mammec dd-ssfaqan ijj n weryaz zeg yiḍeṣ nnes.  
\v 2 Netta inna ayi: “Min teẓrid?” Necc nniɣ: “Necc ẓriɣ, u xzar, ijj n řqendiř n wureɣ marra, u \add aqa din\add* ijj n ṭṭebṣi n zzect x uzeǧif nnes u xas sebɛa n řefnarat, sebɛa \add sennej i\add* sebɛa n ibuḍen i řefnarat \add i iǧan\add* x uzeǧif nnes  
\v 3 u zzates \add aqa din\add* tnayen n izemmuren, ijj ɣar uɣezdis afusi n ṭṭebṣi \add n zzect\add* u ijj ɣar uzeřmaḍ nnes.”   
\m
\v 4 Necc arriɣ-dd u ssiwřeɣ ak-d lmalak nni kidi issawařen, nniɣ: “Sidi inu, min ɛnant tmesřayin-a?”  
\v 5 Lmalak nni kidi issawařen, yarra-dd, inna ayi: “Ma war tessined cek, min ɛnant tmesřayin-a?” Necc nniɣ: “Lla, \add a\add* sidi inu!”   
\m
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd uca issiweř-dd akidi, inna: “Wa d awař n SIDI i Zarubbabil, \add awař\add* nni iqqar: ‘War iǧi s jjehd uřa s lɛunf, maca ad yiři s Arruḥ inu!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat. \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt Ḥuc. 1:7\x*  
\v 7 Min teɛnid cek, \add a\add* adrar ameqqran? Ad tdewřed d ict n řwaṭa zzat i wudem n Zarubbabil, maɣar netta ad dd-issuffeɣ aẓru n nnej s iɣuyyan ijehden: ‘Arḍa, arḍa ad ɣares yiři!’”   
\m
\v 8 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 9 “Ifassen n Zarubbabil ssarsen dsas i Taddart-a, ifassen nnes ad tt kemmřen, maḥend ad tessnem aqa SIDI n řɛeskarat issekk ayi-dd ɣarwem.  
\v 10 Maɣar man wen isseḥqaran ass n tmesřayin timeẓyanin? Sebɛa \add n tiṭṭawin\add* nni ggur ad farḥen, xmi ɣa ẓaren aẓru n teɣmart deg ufus n Zarubbabil, aqa atent tiṭṭawin n SIDI nni ittekken marra tammurt.”   
\m
\v 11 Necc arreɣ-dd, nniɣ as: “Mana tnayen n izemmuren nni \add din\add* ɣar uɣezdis afusi d uẓermaḍ n řqendiř?”  
\v 12 Arniɣ ṭṭfeɣ deg wawař, nniɣ as: “Min ɛnan tnayen n řefruɛ n uzemmur \add nni iǧan\add* sennej i tnayen n iqudas n wureɣ, d yinni ittfarraɣen \add zzect s tinta nnes n\add* wureɣ \add s tnayen n iqudas nni\add*?”  
\v 13 Netta issawař-dd ɣari, inna: “Ma war tessined cek min ɛnan ina?” Necc nniɣ: “Lla, \add a\add* sidi inu!”  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Ina d tnayen n iḥenjiren i ittwadehnen s zzect nni ibedden zzat i Sidi n marra tammurt.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss setta - Adlis ittwannḍen iṭṭawen  
\m
\v 1 Ssgeɛɛdeɣ tiṭṭawin inu twařa nneɣni uca ẓriɣ, u xzar, aqa \add din\add* \bd ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen iṭṭaw\bd*.  
\v 2 Netta inna ayi: “Min tᵉttwařid cek?” Necc nniɣ: “Necc ttwařiɣ ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen iṭṭaw s yijj n tuzzeggart n ɛicrin n iɣaǧen d ict n tiru n ɛecra n iɣaǧen.”  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “Ta d nneɛřet nni i ɣa iffɣen x marra tammurt. Maɣar marra wenni i ɣa yacaren, ad ittwaqḍeɛ zi ssibbet n min yuran x uɣezdis-a u kuř ijj wenni i ɣa ijjaǧen ẓur ad ittwaqḍeɛ zi ssibbet n min yuran x uɣezdis nneɣni.  
\v 4 Necc ad arreɣ nneɛřet ad dd-teffeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, ḥima ad dd-tas di taddart n uceffar u di taddart n yinni ittjaǧan ẓur s Yisem inu. Nettat ad tessens di řwest n taddart nnes u nettat ad tt yecc s ukeccuḍ nnes d iẓra nnes.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss sebɛa - Tamɣart di ifa  
\m
\v 5 Iffeɣ-dd lmalak nni kidi issawařen, inna ayi: “Sgeɛɛed tiṭṭawin nnec u xzar min \add din\add* dd-ittbanen!”  
\v 6 Necc nniɣ: “Manawya?” Netta inna: “Wa d \bd řmud n ifa\bd* nni dd-ittbanen.” \add Xenni\add* inna: “Ta d furma nsen x marra tammurt.”  
\v 7 U xzar, aqa tᵉttwassgeɛɛed tqebbart n řexfif \add d taqurarirt\add* u teqqim ict n temɣart di řwesṭ n ifa.  
\v 8 Netta inna: “Ta d taɛeffant!” uca inḍar i-tt \add ɛawed\add* deg ifa nni uca inḍar aẓru n řexfif x uqemmum nnes.  
\v 9 Necc ssgeɛɛdeɣ tiṭṭawin inu uca ẓriɣ, u xzar tnayen n temɣarin usint-i-dd ɣar zzat u asemmiḍ iccur afriwen nsent. Nitenti tuɣa ɣarsent afriwen am wafriwen n ubellarj u nitenti ssgeɛɛdent ifa \add nni\add* jar temmurt d ujenna.  
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ i lmalak nni kidi issawařen: “Mani ɣa raḥent ak-d ifa-ya?”  
\v 11 Netta inna ayi: “Maḥend ad as bnan ict n taddart di temmurt n Cinar. Mařa tᵉttwakemmeř, ad tᵉttwassbedd din deg wemcan nnes.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Aneggar n tmeẓriwt wiss amezwaru - Arebɛa n ikarruten  
\m
\v 1 Necc ssgeɛɛdeɣ tiṭṭawin inu twařa nneɣni, u xzar, aqa arebɛa n ikarruten ffɣen-dd zi jar tnayen n idurar u idurar \add nni\add* tuɣa d idurar n nnḥas.  
\v 2 Ɣar ukarru amezwaru \add tuɣa din\add* iysan d izeggʷaɣen, ɣar ukarru wiss tnayen iysan d ibarcanen,  
\v 3 ɣar ukarru wiss třata iysan d icemřařen u ɣar ukarru wiss arebɛa iysan d iqarqacen, \add aqa aten d iysan\add* jehden.  
\v 4 Necc arriɣ-dd, nniɣ i lmalak nni kidi issawařen: “Min ɛnan ina, \add a\add* sidi inu?”   
\m
\v 5 Yarra-dd lmalak, inna ayi: “Ina d arebɛa n isemmiḍen n ujenna nni dd-itteffɣen zi mani bedden zzat i SIDI n marra tammurt.  
\v 6 Inni s iysan ibarcanen ad ffɣen ɣar temmurt n Ccamal u \add iysan\add* icemřařen ad ten ḍeffaren, uca \add iysan\add* iqarqacen ad ffɣen ɣar temmurt n Ljanub.”  
\v 7 \add Iysan\add* ijehden ffɣen, arzun ad ẓwan tammurt, \add maɣar\add* Netta inna: “Ffɣem, ẓwam tammurt!” U nitni ẓwan temmurt.  
\v 8 Netta iřaɣa ayi-dd, inna: “Xzar, \add iysan\add* nni iffɣen ɣar temmurt n Ccamal, aqa ssareyyḥen Arruḥ inu di temmurt n Ccamal.” \f ◼ \fr 6:8 \ft \+fk ssareyyḥen Arruḥ inu\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini belli řḥukm nni ssiwḍen iysan ibarcanen x Temmurt n Ccamal issjjiwen Arruḥ n Arebbi. Aqa řḥakamat nnes iseggden umi Netta d Amsegged.\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ttaj i ukehhan ameqqran  
\m
\v 9 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 10 “Ksi tiwhibin zeg ayt n lmenfa, zi Ḥalim, Ṭubiya d Yadaɛya u ruḥ dinni \add uřa d\add* cek \bd deg wass nni\bd* u adef ɣar taddart n Yuciya, mmis n Ṣafanya, \add ɣar taddart\add* i ɣares dd-yusin zi Babil. \f ◼ \fr 6:10 \ft \+fk Ṣafanya\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni t issnuffaren SIDI’.\f*  
\v 11 Ksi nnuqart d wureɣ, egg \add zzaysen\add* ttijan u sars \add i-ten\add* x uzeǧif n Yahucaɛ, mmis n Yahuṣadaq, arrays n ikehhanen,  
\v 12 u siweř akides, ini as:  
\b  
\m ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: Xzar, ijj n weryaz, ‘AƔEDDU’ d Isem nnes. Netta ad dd-iffeɣ zeg wemcan nnes u Netta ad ibna Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI.  
\v 13 Netta ad ibna Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI u ad yarḍ lɛaḍama. Netta ad iqqim u ad iḥkem x řɛarc nnes u Netta ad yiři d akehhan x řɛarc nnes u ad yiři jar asen ccwar s řehna.’   
\b  
\m
\v 14 Ttijan ad iřin i Ḥalim, Ṭubiya, Yadaɛya d Ḥayn, mmis n Ṣafanya, d řidaret di Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 6:14 \ft \+fk Ḥayn\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘řxaḍar’.\f*  
\v 15 Zi řaggʷaj ad dd-asen \add iwdan\add* u nitni ad bnan Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI u kenniw ad tessnem aqa SIDI n řɛeskarat issekk ayi-dd ɣarwem. \add Aya\add* ad imsar, mařa kenniw tᵉttesřam s tidett ɣar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nwem.” \x ◘ \xo 6:15 \xt Ḥag. 2:7 \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Iseqsiten x ussan n uẓummi - Awař amezwaru n SIDI  
\m
\v 1 \bd Imsar deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n ujeǧid Dariyus,\bd* \add řami\add* dd-yusa wawař n SIDI ɣar Zakariyya, \bd deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* wiss arebɛa n uyur wiss tesɛa, deg \+bdit uyur\+bdit* n Kisluw,\bd*  
\v 2 \add aqa\add* issekk \add řgens n\add* Bayt-Il Caraṣir d Rajam-Malik d yeryazen nnes maḥend ad ttaren arḍa zzat i wudem n SIDI,  
\v 3 umi ssawařen ak-d ikehhanen, inni \add iǧan\add* di Taddart n SIDI n řɛeskarat, u ak-d inabiyyen, qqaren: “Ma ad arniɣ deg uyur wiss xemsa ad ruɣ u ad ɛezřeɣ ixef inu am mammec t tteggeɣ řexxu ɛad aṭṭas n iseggʷusa?”   
\b  
\m
\v 4 \bd Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI n řɛeskarat, inna:\bd*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 “Siweř ak-d marra řgens u ak-d ikehhanen, ini: Řami kenniw tẓummem u tewtim x idmaren nwem \add zeg wecḍan\add*, deg uyur wiss xemsa u deg uyur wiss sebɛa, u man aya řexxu ɛad aṭṭas n iseggʷusa, ma tẓummem kenniw \add xenni\add* i Necc, \add s tidett\add* i Necc?  
\v 6 Řami teccim u řami teswim, ma war ticcim \add i yixef nwem\add* u ma war tiswim \add i yixef nwem\add*?  
\v 7 Ma war tuɣi iřiq ad yiři zi ssibbet n wawařen i ijja SIDI ad ttwabarrḥen s ufus n inabiyyen n zic umi tuɣa teqqim Urcalim \add ɛad\add* s imezdaɣ di řhudnet ak-d tneddam i d as dd-innḍen, u řami tuɣa \add ɛad\add* imezdaɣ di \add Tammurt n\add* Ljanub u di Temmurt Iwaṭan?”   
\b  
\m
\v 8 \bd Yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Zakariyya, inna:\bd*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 \bd “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat\bd*, i iqqaren: ‘Ḥekmem s ijj n řḥukm iseggden u ggem s tmexsiwt icewwaren d arreḥmet ijj ak-d wenneɣni.  
\v 10 War ḥeṣṣarem tajjač uřa d ayujiř niɣ řbarrani uřa d ameẓřuḍ, u war ttejjim uřa d ijj ad ixarreṣ di řɣar ḍidd i umas deg wuř nnes!’ \x ◘ \xo 7:10 \xt Uf. 22:22\x*  
\v 11 \add Maca\add* nitni ugin ad wcen taynit u nitni ggin marra s řmeqřub u bellɛen imezzuɣen nsen, ḥima war ttesřin.  
\v 12 Nitni ssqesḥen uř nsen am yijj n umesmir, maḥend war ttesřin Ccariɛa d wawařen nni dd-issekk SIDI n řɛeskarat s Arruḥ nnes s ufus n inabiyyen n zic, ařami dd-yusa ijj n uduqqez d ameqqran n weɣḍab n SIDI n řɛeskarat.  
\v 13 Aqa imsar am mammec iřaɣa Netta \add zic\add*, \add maca\add* nitni war sřin ca. S uyenni řaɣan \add řexxu\add* nitni u Necc war ttesřiɣ ca, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat. \x ◘ \xo 7:13 \xt Awřn. 1:28; Ica. 1:15; Irm. 11:11; 14:12\x*  
\v 14 Necc ad ten zuzzareɣ x marra řegnus nni tuɣa war ssinen u awarni asen ad tᵉttwaxarreb temmurt, uřa d ijj \add ɛad\add* war \add xas\add* iẓekkwi u uřa d ijj \add ɛad\add* war dd-iddikkwiř. Nitni arrin tammurt iɛizzen d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Awař wiss tnayen n SIDI - SIDI ad ibarek Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 \bd Yusa-dd \+bdit ɣari\+bdit* wawař n SIDI n řɛeskarat, inna:\bd*   
\b  
\m
\v 2 \bd “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd* ‘S wasam d ameqqran usmeɣ zi Ṣihyun, s wesɛar tameqqrant usmeɣ di ṭṭweɛ nnes.’\x ◘ \xo 8:2 \xt Zak. 1:14\x*  
\v 3 \bd Ammu i iqqar SIDI:\bd* ‘Necc ɛeqbeɣ-dd ɣar Ṣihyun u ad zedɣeɣ di řwesṭ n Urcalim uca Urcalim ad as řaɣan ‘Tandint n tidett!’, u adrar n SIDI n řɛeskarat ad as inin ‘Adrar Iqeddsen!’ \x ◘ \xo 8:3 \xt Asa. 14:1-5\x*   
\m
\v 4 \bd Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd* ‘Ad iřin ɛawed iwessura d twessura deg wazzayen n Urcalim. \add Kuř\add* aryaz ad ɣares tiři teɣɣarct nnes deg ufus nnes zi ssibbet n waṭṭas n wussan \add i ɣa iddar\add*.  
\v 5 Azzayen n tendint ad dewřen ccuren s iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin i ittiraren deg wazzayen nnes.’   
\m
\v 6 \bd Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd* ‘Maɣar d řeɛjeb qaɛ di tiṭṭawin n min iqqimen n řgens-a deg wussan nni, ma ad yiři aya uřa i Necc d řeɛjeb qaɛ?’, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.   
\m
\v 7 \bd Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd* ‘Xzarem, Necc ad ssnejmeɣ řgens inu zi temmurt n wenqar \add n tfuct\add* u zi temmurt n uɣeǧi n tfuct,  
\v 8 u Necc ad ten awyeɣ din ḥima ad zedɣen di Urcalim. Nitni ad iřin d řgens i Necc u Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI i nitni, di tidett u di tsegda.’   
\m
\v 9 \bd Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd* ‘Meḥḍem ifassen nwem, kenniw inni isřin deg wussan-a awařen-a zeg uqemmum n inabiyyen nni \add din iǧan\add* deg wass nni di ittwassars dsas n Taddart n SIDI n řɛeskarat, maḥend ad \add xas\add* tᵉttwabna Zzawect Tameqqrant zi jdid.  
\v 10 Maɣar qbeř i wussan nni war iqqim walu zi řmunet n bnadem u ict n řebhimet war dd-tᵉttawi walu u wenni dd-iffɣen d wenni dd-idewřen, war yiwi řaman zi ssibbet n řeɛdu, \add maɣar\add* Necc ssekkareɣ \add kuř\add* ijj x jjar nnes. \f ◼ \fr 8:10 \ft \+fk \+bdit kuř\+bdit* ijj x jjar nnes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘aryaz x jjar nnes’.\f*  
\v 11 \add Řexxu\add* maca Necc war ttiřiɣ i min iqqimen n řgens-a am wussan imezwura, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.  
\v 12 Maɣar zzariɛet n řehna, tazayart, ad tewc řɣiǧet nnes u tammurt ad tewc ṣṣabet nnes u ajenna ad iwc nnda nnes u Necc ad wceɣ marra aya d tasɣart i min iqqimen n řgens-a.  
\v 13 Ad imsar, aqa am mammec tuɣa kenniw d nneɛřet jar regnus, \add kenniw, a\add* taddart n Yahuda d taddart n Israil, aqa Necc ad kenniw ssnejmeɣ u ad iřiɣ d lbaraka i kenniw. War tteggʷedem, meḥḍem ifassen nwem!’   
\m
\v 14 \bd Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd* ‘Am mammec Necc xarrṣeɣ ad awem ggeɣ řɣar, řami d ayi ssfugmen řejdud nwem, \bd ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat\bd*, u Necc war ndimeɣ \add zi man aya\add*,  
\v 15 ammu i dd-dewřeɣ Necc \add řexxu\add* ad xarrṣeɣ deg wussan-a maḥend ad ggeɣ řxar di Urcalim u di taddart n Yahuda. War tteggʷedem ca!  
\v 16 Tina d timesřayin i kenniw ittxeṣṣan ad tent teggem: Siwřem tidett kuř ijj ak-d jjar nnes, carrɛem di tewwura nwem s tidett u s yijj n řḥukm iřiqqen. \x ◘ \xo 8:16 \xt Afa. 4:25\x*  
\v 17 War ttejjim ad ixarreṣ ijj n weryaz di řɣar x jjar nnes u war ttexsem tajaǧit ẓur, maɣar Necc carrheɣ marra aya!’, iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt Zak. 5:3, 4; 7:10\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 18 \bd Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI n řɛeskarat, inna:\bd*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 \bd “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd* ‘Aẓummi n uyur wiss arebɛa u aẓummi \add n uyur\add* wiss xemsa u aẓummi \add n uyur\add* wiss sebɛa u aẓummi \add n uyur\add* wiss ɛecra ad dewřen d řefraḥet u d warceq i taddart n Yahuda. Ad iřin d řeɛyudat cnan. Xsem tidett d řehna!’   
\m
\v 20 \bd Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd* ‘Aqa řegnus uřa d imezdaɣ n waṭṭas n tneddam ad dd-asen ɛad \add danita\add*! \x ◘ \xo 8:20 \xt Ica. 2:2, Irm. 16:19, Mixa 4:1, Zak. 8:2\x*  
\v 21 Imezdaɣ n ict \add n tendint\add* ad raḥen ɣar imezdaɣ n ict \add n tendint nneɣnit\add*, ad inin: Jjem aneɣ ad neṭṭef abrid ḥima ad nettar \add zzat i\add* wudem n SIDI u ḥima ad narzu SIDI n řɛeskarat. Uřa d necc ad raḥeɣ.  
\v 22 Aṭṭas n iyduden d waṭṭas n řegnus ijehden ad dd-asen ḥima ad arzun x wudem n SIDI n řɛeskarat di Urcalim u ḥima ad ttaren arḍa zzat i wudem n SIDI.’   
\m
\v 23 \bd Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat:\bd* ‘Deg wussan nni ad imsar, aqa ɛecra n yeryazen, zi marra tutlayin n řegnus ad ṭṭfen, \add wah,\add* ad ṭṭfen abeḥřuř n ijj n weryaz d Uday, ad inin: ‘Neccin ad nraḥ akidwem, maɣar nesřa aqa AREBBI akidwem!’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\m
\v 1 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden n wawař n SIDI x temmurt n Ḥadrax,\bd*  
\m \bd \+bdit řḥukm\+bdit* nni yarsan x Dimacq.\bd*  
\b  
\m \qt “Maɣar SIDI iḥeṭṭa x bnadem\qt*  
\m \qt u x marra tiqebbař n Israil,\qt*   
\m
\v 2 \qt uřa x Ḥamat i-tt-dd-iřesqen,\qt*  
\m \qt x Ṣur d Ṣidun,\qt*  
\m \qt waxxa nitenti d timiɣisin aṭṭas.\qt*   
\m
\v 3 \qt Tebna Ṣur ijj n lbaraj i yixef nnes\qt*  
\m \qt u teyru nnuqart am tɛejjajt\qt*  
\m \qt d wureɣ iqquren am ubeǧaɛ n imesraq.\qt*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Xzar, Sidi inu ad tt iṭṭef,\qt*  
\m \qt ad iwwet lbaraj nnes ɣar řebḥar,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad tt tecc tmessi.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 \qt “Ackelun ad tt tẓar, ad tedweř teggʷed,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu\+tl* uřa d Ɣazza, ad tarjij aṭṭas,\qt*  
\m \qt uřa d Ɛaqrun, maɣar ad ifceř uraji nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad ittwateḥḥa ujeǧid zi Ɣazza\qt*  
\m \qt u \+tl di tandint n\+tl* Acqalun\qt*  
\m \qt war dayes tzeddeɣ \+tl ɛad\+tl* uřa d ijjen.\qt*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Mmis n řeḥram ad izdeɣ di Acdud\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad teḥḥiɣ nnfaxet n Ifilisṭiniyyen.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 9:6 \ft \+fk ad teḥḥiɣ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad qeḍɛeɣ’.\f*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Necc ad ksiɣ idammen zeg uqemmum nnes\qt*  
\m \qt uřa d nnɛawat zi jar tiɣmas nnes\qt*  
\m \qt u ammu i ɣa iqqim uřa d netta\qt*  
\m \qt i AREBBI nneɣ.\qt*  
\m \qt Netta ad yiři am yijj n wemɣar di Yahuda\qt*  
\m \qt u Ɛaqrun am yijj n Uyabusi.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Necc ad ggeɣ řmargeḥ inu\qt*  
\m \qt deg wenneḍ n Taddart inu,\qt*  
\m \qt ḍidd n wenni i ɣa iẓwan\qt*  
\m \qt u ḍidd n wenni dd ɣa idewřen,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima wenni iḥeṣṣaren\qt*  
\m \qt war xas iɛeddu ca ɛad,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar řexxu ẓřiɣ \+tl t\+tl* s tiṭṭawin inu.”\qt*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ajeǧid i dd ɣa yasen n Siḥyun  
\m
\v 9 \qt “Farḥ, \+tl a\+tl* yeǧis n Ṣihyun,\qt*  
\m \qt sřiwřew, \+tl a\+tl* yeǧis n Urcalim!\qt*  
\m \qt Xzar, Ajeǧid nnem yusa-dd ɣarem,\qt*  
\m \qt Netta d amsegged\qt*  
\m \qt u aqa yarḍ arruḍ n usenjem,\qt*  
\m \qt Netta d amwaḍeɛ,\qt*  
\m \qt inya x ijj n weɣyuř,\qt*  
\m \qt x ijj n wezɛuq, asnus n ict n teɣyuč.\qt*   
\m
\v 10 \qt Necc ad qḍiɣ ikarruten \+tl n umenɣi\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt zi Ifrayim\qt*  
\m \qt uřa d iysan zi Urcalim.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad ittwaqřeɛ uřa d řqews n umenɣi.\qt*  
\m \qt Netta ad ibarreḥ s řehna i regnus\qt*  
\m \qt u ṣṣulṭa nnes ad tiři\qt*  
\m \qt zi řebḥar ař řebḥar,\qt*  
\m \qt zeg iɣzar \+tl n Lfuraṭ\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ař ineggura n temmurt.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 \qt “\+tl Wah\+tl* uřa d cem, \+tl a yeǧis n Ṣihyun\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt zi ssibbet n idammen n Řɛahd nnem\qt*  
\m \qt fekkeɣ-dd imeḥbas nnem\qt*  
\m \qt zeg wanu yuẓɣen i war di ǧin waman.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:11 \xt Mt. 26:28; Lk. 22:20; Rum. 9:3, 4; Rum. 11:25, 26, 27; 1 Kur. 11:25; Ɛbr. 9:19, 20, 21.\x*   
\m
\v 12 \qt Ɛeqbem ɣar lburj nwem,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl kenniw\+tl* imeḥbas inni ɣar iǧa řayas.\qt*  
\m \qt Uřa d ass-a Necc ttbarrḥeɣ:\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa Necc ad ɣarem dd-arreɣ\qt*  
\m \qt tnayen n tseqqar,\qt*   
\m
\v 13 \qt maɣar Necc ad meḥḍeɣ Yahuda\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl am ijj n řqews\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt u ad ggeɣ Ifrayim x řqews.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc ad ssekkareɣ\qt*  
\m \qt iḥenjiren nnem, \+tl a\+tl* Ṣihyun,\qt*  
\m \qt ḍidd i iḥenjiren nnec, \+tl a\+tl* Yawan,\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad cek arreɣ\qt*  
\m \qt am ssif n ijj n bu-teɣruḍt.”\qt* \f ◼ \fr 9:13 \ft \+fk Yawan\ft  - ixs ad yini Lyunan n zic.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 \qt “SIDI ad iban sennej nsen\qt*  
\m \qt u fřitcat nnes ad iřint\qt*  
\m \qt ttwessgent am wassam\qt*  
\m \qt u Sidi inu, SIDI,ْ\qt*  
\m \qt ad isuḍ deg uyicc n icarri,\qt*  
\m \qt ad yuyur ak-d tḥaryaḍin\qt*  
\m \qt n usemmiḍ n ljanub.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:14 \xt Nḥm. 2:6\x*   
\m
\v 15 \qt SIDI n řɛeskarat ad ten issduriy.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni ad ccen,\qt*  
\m \qt ad ddzen iẓra n iǧiy uca ad swen,\qt*  
\m \qt ad ggen ddriz am ɣar binu\qt*  
\m \qt u ad dewřen ccuren\qt*  
\m \qt am ṭṭawya n urucci,\qt*  
\m \qt am tɣemmar n uɛalṭar.\qt*   
\m
\v 16 \qt SIDI, AREBBI nwem\qt*  
\m \qt ad ten issenjem\qt* \bdit deg wass nni\bdit*  
\m \qt am wuǧi n řgens nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar nitni \+tl amecnaw\+tl* iẓra \+tl iɣřan\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt x ijj n ttaj \+tl igellden\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ittissiqen x temmurt nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 17 \qt Maɣar mechař imɣar ad yiři řxar \+tl nnes\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt u mechař imɣar ad yiři waẓři \+tl nnes\+tl*!\qt*  
\m \qt Imendi ad isseɣmi iḥudriyyen\qt*  
\m \qt uřa binu n jdid tiɛzariyyin.”\qt*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\s1 Aɛdař n Yahuda d Israil  
\m
\v 1 \qt “Ttarem anẓar zi SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt di řweqt n wenẓar n tefsut.\qt*  
\m \qt SIDI ittegg assamen,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl wah,\+tl* Netta ad asen iwc\qt*  
\m \qt ibuda n wenẓar,\qt*  
\m \qt i kuř ijj n wefsu deg iyyar.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 10:1 \ft \+fk anẓar n tafsut\ft  - anẓar n tefsut di Ccarq Ameřwasu iccat qbeř řweqt n tmeyra deg uyur n mars d wavril.\f*   
\m
\v 2 \qt Maɣar řexyařat n l’aṣnam ssawařen řɣecc,\qt*  
\m \qt u igezzanen ttwařan ixarriqen\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ttɛawaden tirja icemmten,\qt*  
\m \qt nitni ssfewwajen s řeɛwin.\qt*  
\m \qt X uya i ttwassiggʷejen am wuǧi,\qt*  
\m \qt ttwaḥṣaren, minzi ameksaw war din iǧi.”\qt* \f ◼ \fr 10:2 \ft \+fk ameksaw\ft  - niɣ ‘aniči’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:2 \xt Amb. 5:6\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 3 \qt “X imeksawen yarɣa weɣḍab inu\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad xeǧṣeɣ iɣayḍen,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar SIDI n řɛeskarat\qt*  
\m \qt ad issijj x tḥimart nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt x taddart n Yahuda,\qt*  
\m \qt u Netta ad ten isedd\qt*  
\m \qt am uyis nnes ittissiqen ɣar umenɣi.\qt*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Zzayes aẓru n teɣmart,\qt*  
\m \qt zzayes řewted,\qt*  
\m \qt zzayes řqews \+tl n umenɣi\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt ad zzayes dd-ffɣen \+tl xenni\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt marra imzeyyaren jmiɛ.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:4 \xt Ica. 28:16; Ica. 22:23\x*   
\m
\v 5 \qt Nitni marra ad dewřen\qt*  
\m \qt am ayt n bu-teɣruḍt\qt*  
\m \qt inni deg umenɣi ad ɛefsen\qt*  
\m \qt x ubeǧaɛ di zznaqi.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Wah\+tl*, nitni ad mmenɣen,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar SIDI ad yiři akidsen,\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad seḍḥan inni inyin x yeysan.\qt*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Necc ad ssjehdeɣ taddart n Yahuda\qt*  
\m \qt u ad ssnejmeɣ taddart n Yusuf\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad asen wceɣ tazeddiɣt,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar Necc arreḥmeɣ daysen\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad iřin axmi Necc\qt*  
\m \qt war ten nḍareɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad ɣarsen sřeɣ.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 \qt “\+tl Inni n\+tl* Ifrayim ad iřin\qt*  
\m \qt am yijj n bu-teɣruḍt\qt*  
\m \qt u uř nsen ad ifarḥ am ɣar binu,\qt*  
\m \qt u iḥenjiren nsen\qt*  
\m \qt ad t ẓaren u ad farḥen,\qt*  
\m \qt uř nsen ad ifarḥ di SIDI.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Necc ad xasen ṣeffareɣ\qt*  
\m \qt u ad ten ssmuneɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar Necc fdiɣ ten,\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad dd-dewřen deg waṭṭas,\qt*  
\m \qt am mammec ten tuɣa deg waṭṭas.\qt*   
\m
\v 9 \qt Necc ad ten zarɛeɣ jar řegnus\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad ayi idaren\qt*  
\m \qt di jjwayeh iggʷejjen.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Xenni\+tl* ad ddaren ak-d iḥenjiren nsen\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad dd-dewřen.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt Ḥiz. 37:13-14\x*   
\m
\v 10 \qt Necc ad ten jjeɣ ad dd-ɛeqben zi Misřa,\qt*  
\m \qt ad ten dd-ssmuneɣ zi Accur\qt*  
\m \qt u ad ten dd-awyeɣ ɣar temmurt n Jilɛad\qt*  
\m \qt u \+tl ɣar\+tl* Lubnan,\qt*  
\m \qt maca aya war ten ittqeddi.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:10 \xt Irm. 22:6; Ḥuc. 9:3; Zak. 10:11\x*   
\m
\v 11 \qt Netta ad iẓwa řebḥar n řeḥṣaret nsen\qt*  
\m \qt u ad iwwet řemwaj n řebḥar\qt*  
\m \qt u marra imucan yuǧɣen\qt*  
\m \qt n iɣzar \+tl n Nil\+tl* ad aẓɣen.\qt*  
\m \qt Nnfaxet n Accur ad tᵉttwasswaḍeɛ,\qt*  
\m \qt u azeǧaḍ n Misřa ad ittwaweddar.\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt Necc ad ten ssjehdeɣ di SIDI\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad uyuren deg Yisem nnes!”,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu i\+tl* iqqar SIDI.\qt*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Ameksaw Aṣebḥan d yimeksawen iɛeffanen d umeksaw abuhaři  
\m
\v 1 \qt “Arzem tiwwura nnec, \+tl a\+tl* Lubnan,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maḥend\+tl* timessi ad tecc tineglin nnec.\qt*   
\m
\v 2 \qt Ru, \+tl a tacejjart\+tl* n umerzi,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar tangelt tewḍa,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar ticejjura \+tl nni\+tl* ijehden\qt*  
\m \qt ttwareddǧent!\qt*  
\m \qt Rut, \+tl a\+tl* ticejjura n řbeǧuḍ n Bacan,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar azɣar immcubbcen iwḍa.”\qt* \f ◼ \fr 11:2 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’. \fk amerzi\ft  - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 3 \qt “\+tl Sřem\+tl* i řḥess n tɣuyyit n imeksawen,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar aɛuǧi nsen ittwareddeǧ,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl sřem\+tl* i řḥess n uzehhar\qt*  
\m \qt n weyraden imeẓyanen,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar řɛezz n L’Urdun ittwareddeǧ.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI inu: ‘Arwes uǧi nni umi ɣa ɣarṣen,  
\v 5 inni ten imellken neqqen ten břa ma ad ttwaɛaqben, inni \add ten imellken\add* zzenzen ten, qqaren: Ad ittwabarek SIDI, aqa necc dewřeɣ ɣari agřa! Imeksawen nsen war d asen zziǧizen.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “Xenni Necc war d ayi zziǧizen ɛad imezdaɣ n temmurt, iqqar SIDI. Xzar, Necc ad wceɣ i iwdan kuř ijj deg ufus n jjar nnes u deg ufus n ujeǧid nnes, u nitni ad ɛefsen x temmurt u Necc war \add ten\add* ttfekkeɣ ca zeg ufus nsen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 7 “Necc arewseɣ uǧi tinni umi ɣa ɣarṣen, maɣar nitenti d uǧi ittwaḥsaren. Necc ksiɣ i Yixef inu tnayen n tᵉɣɣaryen. Ict ggiɣ as ‘Řxaḍar!’ u tenneɣni ggiɣ as ‘Taɣruḍt!’, u \add ammu i\add* arwseɣ Necc uǧi.”   
\b  
\m
\v 8 “Deg ijj n uyur tteḥḥiɣ třata zeg imeksawen. Řeɛmar inu war izemmar ad ten tarbu \add ɛad\add* uca uřa d řeɛmar nsen icarh ayi ɛawed.  
\v 9 Necc nniɣ: Necc war kenniw arekkwseɣ! Min immuten, ejj \add i-t\add* ad immet u min ihellken, ejj \add i-t\add* ad ittwahellek, u jjem inni iqqimen ad ccen aysum ijj n wenneɣni.  
\v 10 Necc ksiɣ taɣɣarct inu ‘Rxaḍar’, uca arẓiɣ tt maḥend ad arẓeɣ ammu řɛahd inu nni ggiɣ ak-d marra řegnus.  
\v 11 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* idweř \add řɛahd\add* yarreẓ u ammu i ssnen wuǧi ittwaḥṣaren nni d ayi iḥeṭṭan, aqa aya tuɣa d ijj n wawař n SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 12 “Necc nniɣ asen: ‘Mařa aya mliḥ di tiṭṭawin nwem, wcem ayi řmunet inu, u mařa lla, jjem t!’ \add Xenni\add* weznen řmunet inu: třatin n \add řweznat n\add* nnuqart. \x ◘ \xo 11:12 \xt Uf. 21:32; Mt. 26:15; 27:9\x*  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi SIDI: ‘Nḍar \add řmunet\add* nni ɣar bu-třaxt, ttaman \add nni\add* ‘iṣebḥen’ inni d ayi ggin ttaman!’ U necc ksiɣ třatin n řweznat n nnuqart uca nḍareɣ tent ɣar bu-třaxt di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 14 \add Řexdenni\add* arẓiɣ Necc taɣɣarct inu nneɣni \add tenni ggiɣ as\add* ‘Taɣruḍt’ maḥend ad arẓeɣ \add ammu\add* tawmat jar Yahuda d Israil.”   
\b  
\m
\v 15 “SIDI inna ayi: ‘Ksi twařa nneɣnit dduzan n ijj n umeksaw abuhaři,  
\v 16 maɣar Necc ad jjeɣ ad dd-ikkar ijj n umeksaw di temmurt: min iruḥen war yarezzu, min imṭarrcen war t yarezzu, min yarẓen war t issgenfi u min iqqimen ibedd, war t iḥeṭṭi netta. \add Maca\add* netta ad yecc aysum n \add řebhayem\add* iṣeḥḥen u ad asent ikkes ticeḍyin.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 17 \qt “Uct x umeksaw i war isekkwin,\qt*  
\m \qt wenni isemmḥen deg wuǧi!\qt*  
\m \qt Ssif \+tl ad dd-iɛdu\+tl* x uɣiř nnes\qt*  
\m \qt u x tiṭṭ nnes tafusect.\qt*  
\m \qt Aɣiř nnes ad yaẓeɣ marra,\qt*  
\m \qt u tiṭṭ nnes tafusect ad teɛmec marra!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:17 \xt Irm. 23:1; Ḥiz. 34:2; Yḥ. 10:12\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Řeḥṣaret d ufekki d tɣuyyit n wecḍan n Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden n wawař n SIDI x Israil.\bd* SIDI issawař, Netta d wenni ittbezzaɛen ajenna u issrusa dsas n temmurt u issbedda arruḥ n bnadem di daxeř nnes:   
\b  
\m
\v 2 “Xzarem, Necc ad ggeɣ Urcalim d ṭṭebṣi n udewwex i marra řegnus i d as dd-innḍen uca ad dd-yas ṭṭebṣi nni uřa x Yahuda ɣar řeḥṣaret n Urcalim.   
\b  
\m
\v 3 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar aqa Necc ad arreɣ Urcalim d ijj n weẓru ideqřen i marra řegnus. Marra inni yarezzun ad t ssgeɛɛden, ad ssyezmen ixef nsen aṭṭas u marra řegnus n ddunect ad ttwassmunen ḍidd nnes.   
\m
\v 4 \bd Deg wass nni\bd*, iqqar SIDI, ad wteɣ marra iysan s arjef d imnayen nnes s tubbuheřya, \add maca\add* ad qqimeɣ arezzmeɣ tiṭṭawin inu x taddart n Yahuda, \add xmi\add* i ɣa wteɣ marra iysan n řegnus s tuddarɣeč.  
\v 5 Imgewwaden n Yahuda ad inin deg wuř nsen: ‘Imezdaɣ n Urcalim ad iřin d jjehd inu s \add ufus n\add* SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI nsen!’   
\m
\v 6 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ggeɣ imgewwaden n Yahuda am yijj n řmejmar n tmessi di taffa n ukeccuḍ u am yijj n weṣfeḍ jar tiqebbiḍin n imendi u nitni ad ffzen marra řegnus i d asen dd-innḍen, ɣar yefus u ɣar uzeřmaḍ, uca Urcalim ad teqqim ɛad deg wemcan nnes, di Urcalim.  
\v 7 SIDI ad issenjem amezwar iqiḍan n Yahuda ḥima ccan n taddart n Dawud d ccan n imezdaɣ n Urcalim war iddikkwiř d ameqqran aṭṭas qibač i Yahuda.   
\m
\v 8 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad issduriy SIDI imezdaɣ n Urcalim.  
\m \bd Deg wass\bd* nni ad yiři wenni i ɣa innqarḍen jar asen am Dawud uca taddart n Dawud ad tiři am AREBBI, am lmalak n SIDI zzat i wudem nsen.   
\m
\v 9 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar, aqa Necc ad rekkzeɣ ad mḥiɣ marra řegnus i dd ɣa yasen \add i řeḥṣaret\add* ɣar Urcalim.  
\v 10 \add Maca\add* ad farrɣeɣ Arruḥ n arḍa d tẓaǧitin x taddart n Dawud u x imezdaɣ n Urcalim u nitni ad ɣari dd-xzaren wenni di ssnuqqben. Nitni ad xas wten ayejdur am wtin agejdur x uyenni n mmis u ad xas ceḍnen s terzugi am wenni ittecḍinen x \add řmewt n\add* mmis amenzu. \x ◘ \xo 12:10 \xt Ḥiz. 39:29; Yuw. 3:1; Yḥ. 19:37; Asa. 1:7\x*   
\m
\v 11 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad tiři tɣuyyit n wecḍan temɣar di Urcalim, am tɣuyyit n wecḍan n Hadad-Rimmun di teɣzurt n Majiddun. \x ◘ \xo 12:11 \xt 2 Ij. 23:29; 2 Im. 35:22, 24\x*   
\m
\v 12 Tammurt ad tesɣuy zeg wecḍan, kuř řaǧ weḥḥdes.  
\m Řaǧ n taddart n Dawud weḥḥdes  
\m d temɣarin nsen weḥḥedsent,  
\m řaǧ n taddart n Natan weḥḥdes  
\m d temɣarin nsen weḥḥedsent.   
\m
\v 13 Řaǧ n taddart n Lawi weḥḥdes  
\m d temɣarin nsen weḥḥedsent,  
\m řaǧ n Cimɛi weḥḥdes  
\m d temɣarin nsen weḥḥedsent.   
\m
\v 14 Marra řaǧat nneɣni, kuř řaǧ weḥḥdes uřa d timɣarin weḥḥedsent.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Asefṣi d usizdeg n Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ggur ad tedduqqez ict n tařa i taddart n Dawud uřa i imezdaɣ n Urcalim, ḍidd i ddenb u ḍidd i řexmej.   
\m
\v 2 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, Necc ad teḥḥiɣ ismawen n řexyařat n l’aṣnam zi temmurt, \add ḥima\add* war xasen ɛeqqřen ɛad. Uřa d inabiyyen d buḥbeř amengus ad ten ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 13:2 \ft \+fk ad teḥḥiɣ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad qeḍɛeɣ’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 13:2 \xt Aɛwd. 13:6-11; Aɛwd. 18:20. \x*  
\v 3 Ad imsar, mařa ca n ijjen ad inebba, belli babas d yemmas inni t-i-dd ijjin, ad as inin: ‘Cek war ttɣimid teddared, maɣar cek tessiwřed ixarriqen deg isem n SIDI!’ Babas d yemmas inni t-i-dd ijjin, ad t ssnuqqben xmi ɣa inebba. \x ◘ \xo 13:3 \xt Aɛwd. 13:6-11, 18:20\x*   
\m
\v 4 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar aqa inabiyyen ad seḍḥan, kuř ijj x řewḥiy nnes \add i itwařa\add* xmi tuɣa inebba. Nitni war ttiriḍen ca apartessu n ccɛar \add n inabiyyen\add* maḥend ad ssxarrqen.  
\v 5 Netta ad yini ‘Necc war ǧiɣ d anabi, necc d ijj n weryaz wenni ittfeǧḥen iyyar, minzi ikseb ayi ijjen zi temẓi inu.’  
\v 6 Ad as inin: ‘Min ɛnan \add xenni\add* iyezzimen-a deg ifassen nnec?’, ad yini netta: ‘Ammu i wtin ayi di taddart n imɛizzen inu.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 7 “Ssif, kkar x Umeksaw inu u x weryaz nni iǧan d amɛacar inu!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat. Wwet Ameksaw inu uca \add xenni\add* ad immsebḍa wuǧi, \add maca\add* Necc ad arreɣ afus inu \add ɛawed i useřqi\add* tiwwa imuqřiřen.” \x ◘ \xo 13:7 \xt Mt. 26:31; Mk. 14:27\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 “Ad imsar di tammurt marra, iqqar SIDI, aqa tnayen n izeynat ad ttwaqeḍɛen u nitni ad ssuffɣen buḥbeř, \add maca\add* azyen wiss třata ad dayes iqqim.  
\v 9 Azyen wiss třata ad t nḍareɣ di tmessi, uca Necc ad ten ssᵉṣfiɣ am mammec sseṣfan nnuqart u Necc ad ten jarrbeɣ am mammec ttjarraben ureɣ. Nitni ad řaɣan s Yisem inu u Necc ad \add asen\add* sřeɣ. Ad iniɣ: ‘Řgens inu!’ u nitni ad inin: ‘SIDI d AREBBI inu!’” \x ◘ \xo 13:9 \xt Izhd. 50:15; 91:15; 144:15; Yḥ. 20:28; 1 Bṭ. 1:6\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Ahekkwu n SIDI x wedrar n Zzitun  
\m
\v 1 \bd “Xzaret, ad dd-yas ijj n wass i SIDI\bd* i di i ɣa tᵉttwabḍa tkeccaḍt nnem di řwesṭ nnem! \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt Yuw. 2:10, 31; 3:15; Ica. 13:6-13; 24:23; Am. 8:9; Mt. 24:29; Řex. 2:20; Asa. 6:12-13\x*  
\v 2 Necc ad ssmuneɣ marra řegnus i umenɣi ak-d Urcalim. Tandint ad tᵉttwaṭṭef, tudrin ad ttwakeccḍent, timɣarin ad ttwassnuqqbent u azyen n tendint ad ittwandeh di lmenfa, \add maca\add* min iqqimen n řgens war ggur ca ad ittwaqḍeɛ. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt Ica. 13:16\x*  
\v 3 SIDI ad iffeɣ u Netta ad immneɣ ak-d řegnus am deg wass n umenɣi, deg wass n ittmenɣa \add řebda\add* deg wass n wehjam. \x ◘ \xo 14:3 \xt Ica. 42:13\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad bedden iḍaren nnes x wedrar n Zzitun wenni qibač i Urcalim, ɣar ccarq. Adrar n Zzitun ad ittwafeǧeq di tnayen n iziynat, jjihet n ccarq u jjihet n řebḥar, \add maḥend ad din tiři\add* ict n teɣzurt d tameqqrant. Azyen n wedrar ad imeyyeř ɣar ccamal u azyen nneɣni n wedrar ad imeyyeř ɣar ljanub. \x ◘ \xo 14:4 \xt Řex. 1:11\x*  
\v 5 Uca kenniw ad tarewřem zi hekkwu n idurar inu, maɣar taɣzurt n idurar ad dd-taweḍ ař Aṣal u kenniw ad tarewřem am mammec tarewřem kenniw zeg wenhezzi n temmurt deg wussan n Ɛuzziya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, uca SIDI, AREBBI inu, ad dd-yas u marra imqeddasen akidek. \x ◘ \xo 14:5 \xt Ɛam. 1:1\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ggur ad imsar aqa war tᵉttiři tfawt, itran ittissiqen ad tᵉttwakemmcen.  
\v 7 Ad yiři d ijj n wass ittwafarz, ad yiři ittwassen ɣar SIDI. War iǧi d ass uřa d ǧiřet. Ad imsar ɣar řweqt n uɛecci ad tiři tfawt.\x ◘ \xo 14:7 \xt Asa. 21:25\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar aqa aman iddaren ad dd-ffɣen zi Urcalim, azyen zzaysen ɣar řebḥar acarqi u azyen nneɣni ɣar řebḥar n řɣarbi. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa yiři deg unebdu u di tgarst. \f ◼ \fr 14:8 \fq řebḥar\ft  - niɣ ‘il’. \fk tagerst\ft  - niɣ ‘řmecṭa’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 14:8 \xt Ḥiz. 47:1-12; Yuw. 4:18; Asa. 22:1\x*  
\v 9 SIDI ad yiři d ajeǧid x marra tammurt.  
\b  
\m \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad yiři Netta d ayenni n SIDI u Isem nnes d ayenni n Yisem.  
\v 10 Marra tammurt ad tedweř am Řewḍa, zi Jabɛa ař Rimmun, ɣar \add jjihet n\add* ljanub n Urcalim. \add Tandint\add* ad tᵉttwassgeɛɛed u ad dayes zedɣen \add iwdan\add* deg wemcan nnes, zi Tewwart n Binyamin ař amcan n Tewwart i din tuɣa zic, ař tawwart n Teɣmart, u zi lburj n Ḥananiyil ař tisarin n weḥray n ddiřect n ujeǧid.  
\v 11 Nitni ad dayes zedɣen u war ittiři ɛad uřa d ijj n uḥarrem i uteḥḥi, minzi Urcalim ad yiři d amcan mani ɣa zeddɣen di řaman.   
\b  
\m
\v 12 Ta ad tiři d ticti i zi ɣa iwwet SIDI marra řegnus nni immenɣen ak-d Urcalim: Netta ad yarr arrimet n kuř \add bnadem\add* ad ikkiccu am netta ɛad ibedd x iḍaren nnes u tiṭṭawin nnes ad kkiccwent deg ixubac nsen u iřes nnes ad ikkiccu deg uqemmum nnes. \f ◼ \fr 14:12 \ft \+fk aqemmum nnes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘aqemmum nsen’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ggur ad imsar aqa ijj n umxarweḍ d ameqqran zi SIDI ad idweř jar asen, ařami ɣa iṭṭef kuř ijj afus n jjar nnes u \add xenni\add* afus n kuř ijjen ad inneqřeb ḍidd i ufus n jjar nnes.  
\v 14 Ɛad ad immneɣ Yahuda di Urcalim uca ad ttwassmunen wagřa n marra řegnus i d as dd-innḍen: ureɣ d nnuqart d warruḍ aṭṭas s waṭṭas.  
\v 15 Ammu i ɣa tiři \add ɛawed\add* tecti n uyis d usardun d weřɣem d yeɣyař d marra řmař nni \add iǧan\add* di řɛeskarat, aqa ticti-ya \add ad ten teřqef\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* ad imsar aqa marra inni iqqimen zi marra řegnus nni dd-yusin ɣar Urcalim \add i řeḥṣaret\add*, ad geɛɛden zeg useggʷas ař aseggʷas, ḥima ad bendqen zzat i Ujeǧid, i SIDI n řɛeskarat u ḥima ad ɛeyyden Řɛid n Iɛuccuten. \x ◘ \xo 14:16 \xt Ica. 66:23\x*  
\v 17 Ad imsar belli man wen zi řaǧat n temmurt war dd-ittgiɛɛid ca ɣar Urcalim ḥima ad ibendeq i ujeǧid, i SIDI n řɛeskarat, aqa war xas iweṭṭi ca wenẓar.  
\v 18 Mařa řaǧ n Miṣra war dd-igeɛɛed u war dd-tusi ca, \add xenni\add* war xasen \add iccit\add* wenẓar. Ta ad tiři d ticti i zi ɣa iřqef SIDI řegnus nni war din ittgiɛɛiden ca ḥima ad ɛeyyden ficta n Řɛid n Iɛuccuten.  
\v 19 Ta ggur ad tiři d ticti i ddnub n Miṣra uřa d ticti i marra řegnus, inni war din ittgeɛɛeden, ḥima ad ɛeyyden Řɛid n Iɛuccuten.   
\b  
\m
\v 20 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ggur ad yiři x tnaqusin n yeysan ‘D AMQEDDAS i SIDI!’ Ttnajar di Taddart n SIDI ad iřin am ṭṭawyat i urucci zzat i uɛalṭar.  
\v 21 Marra ttnajar di Urcalim u di Yahuda ad iřin qeddsen i SIDI n řɛeskarat u marra inni i dd ɣa yasen ḥima ad qeddmen tiwhibin, ad zzaysent ksin u ad daysent ssnennan.  
\b  
\m \bd Deg wass nni\bd* war \add din\add* ittiři uřa d ijj n Ukenɛani di Taddart n SIDI n řɛeskarat.” \x ◘ \xo 14:21 \xt Ica. 35:8; Yuw. 4:17; Asa. 21:27; 22:15\x*   